Catal Image Vision API Tests Intro

Catal Image Vision API Tests Claudia A Engel Last updated: November 10, 2018 Intro We sampled 1000 random images out of the ~138k that are currently accessioned into SDR and generated labels using the Google Vision API. Code to retreive lables is here: https://github.com/sul-dlss-labs/google-vision-ai Catal is project here: http://catalhoyuk.com For various reasons we had some attrition and ended up with 766 images. Results shown here are based on those.
